result.summary: Attention is power when it is clean. Storm: Choose nourishment, not sedation.

card_notes.note:
Attention is power when it is clean.

Oct watches the trace before it becomes story. It offers presence, not command.

Noise; observe quietly.

Storm: Choose nourishment, not sedation.

You’re numbing with comfort or drifting into dependency.

Don’t be swayed.

Return to the pulse.

Frog is the pulse that says: keep going.

Noise disrupts; simplify.

advice: Information moves fast. External voices amplify. Verify, simplify, choose your signal.
Treat this as guidance, not a fixed outcome.
